					<description><![CDATA[Information The eSuite software provides tools for defining a shopper discount by sub-department. This discount supersedes the regular sub-department discount. If a shopper discount is specified for a certain shopper level, the system will use this discount. Otherwise, it will cascade back to the sub-department discount. This way, a shopper discount must only be specified [&#8230;]]]></description>
		
		
		
